item.title: Wats the latest JDK Download name?
item.dc:creator: @LilXCj LilXCj
item.description:
@LilXCj wrote:

Look in your directory.
Go to My Computer -> C: -> Program Files ->Java -> jdk1.6.0_yourversion

or if you have an (x86) vista/7

My Computer -> C: -> Program Files (x86) -> Java -> jdk1.6.0_yourversion
